description:
Happy Thanksgiving week! As always, Danny is thankful for Real Housewives. This week, TINSLEY IS ENGAGED! Danny ponders what that means for her future on RHONY. Danny also recaps this week's Real Housewives of Atlanta, and tackles what's going on over at RHOD, RHONJ, and RHOC.
